reviewText: this is suppose to be a workout for older people but you'd better be in shape.  I've had this video for a long time and my treadmill broke so I thought I'd try it but it's not for baby boomers.  It's for younger people.  She probably just recycled her old videos for younger people and added baby boomer to it.
Always love working out with DA!
This workout with Denise Austin is good for everybody. You can do it if you are just starting out or if you are 40 +.

The tape does work, but the sound fades in and out.
Our other tapes do not have the same problem.
